breadCrumbs.text: Upload pricing schedules and other documents

title: Upload documents (optional)
line1: You can upload additional documents that will help a supplier to better understand your procurement.
p1: You can upload multiple files, each no larger than 300mb, to a total of 1GB. Acceptable file formats: csv, doc, docx, jpg, jpeg, kml, ods, odt, pdf, png, ppt, pptx, rdf, rtf, txt, xls, xlsx, xml, zip
